When I wrote &#39;box&#39; Rees, I meant any of the automated or manual sweep methods people 
are using, compared to &#39;traditional&#39; EVP methods.  But when it comes to radio sweep 
specifically, for me personally, I get much better results with a manual sweep on my little 
Duracell KP028.  I know everyone&#39;s results differ.  That&#39;s just what works best for me in 
the world of radio.  Excluding Mini/Frank/Joe/etc boxes.  They are creatures unto 
themselves.  ;-)

Margaret

